Chapter: Greeting

 A simple greeting library that demonstrates the full document
 structure: chapter header, prose, sections, and code.

Section: Core

  greet : Text -> Text
  greet (name) = "Hello, " ++ name ++ "!"

  farewell : Text -> Text
  farewell (name) = "Goodbye, " ++ name ++ "."

Section: Formatting

  shout : Text -> Text
  shout (name) = greet name ++ "!!"

